item.title: 2021-03-24 12:00 Time to move! - Örnsköldsvik Developer Meetup
item.description: In this times when many of us is working from home it's more important then ever to get out and move! Are you like me and don't feel like you have the time? Just want to finish this last thing before a quick lunch. (A lunch that could happen in front of the desk)

item.title: 2021-05-26 19:00 ovik.dev - Monthly Meetup - Örnsköldsvik Developer Meetup
